title: (Thurs Early) Lunchbox Finds Out if You Should Tip on To-Go Orders + Elder Vs. Millennial Returns! + Mailbag: Posting Picture of Kids without Permission
itunes:title: (Thurs Early) Lunchbox Finds Out if You Should Tip on To-Go Orders + Elder Vs. Millennial Returns! + Mailbag: Posting Picture of Kids without Permission
description:
Lunchbox gets to the bottom of if we need to be tipping on to-go orders. Eddie and Morgan face off in the return of Elder vs. Millennial. Bobby tries to help a listener dealing with a situation where a picture of their kids was posted on social media without their permission.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
